---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import MoreQuestionsImage from "../../../src/assets/images/more-questions.jpg";
---

<section class="mb-8 mt-0 rounded-2xl bg-base-300 p-2">
	<div class="card flex-col items-center bg-base-100 px-8 py-8 lg:flex-row lg:gap-16">
		<Image
			src={MoreQuestionsImage}
			title="Question Mark - Red Neon Reflection"
			alt="A red neon sign in the shape of a question mark is shown as a reflection with an urban city backdrop."
			class="my-0 aspect-square w-full max-w-sm rounded-lg object-cover shadow-2xl"
		/>
		<div>
			<h3>Still have some questions?</h3>
			<p>
				Didn't find the answers you were looking for? No worries! I encourage you to drop me a
				message through my <a
					href="/contact"
					title="View Contact Page"
					class="btn btn-outline btn-xs text-sm">Contact</a
				> page. I'm always eager to help and address any queries you might have.
			</p>
			<p>
				Email is typically the fastest way to reach me, but I understand different preferences.
				That's why on my <a
					href="/social"
					title="View Social Page"
					class="btn btn-outline btn-xs text-sm">Social</a
				>
				 page, you'll find various other ways to connect with me. Please choose the method that
				suits you best â€“ I look forward to hearing from you!
			</p>
			<a
				href="/contact"
				title="Navigate to Contact Page to Get in Touch"
				class="btn btn-accent w-full">Get In Touch</a
			>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
